def find_lowest_threshold(n, a, b):

    def makePair(z):
        return [(z[i], z[i + 1]) for i in range(0, len(z), 2)]
    sa = set(a)
    xa = list(sa)
    xa.sort(reverse=True)
    zz = [(t, sorted([b[i] for i in range(n) if a[i] == t])) for t in xa]
    lastdp = [[] for i in range(52)]
    lastdp[0] = [(0, 0)]

    def addres(z, t):
        if len(z) == 0:
            z.append(t)
            return
        i = bisect.bisect_right(z, t)
        if i > 0 and z[i - 1][1] >= t[1]:
            return
        if i < len(z) and t[1] >= z[i][1]:
            z[i] = t
            return
        z.insert(i, t)
    for x in zz:
        nowdp = [[] for i in range(52)]
        for i in range(len(lastdp)):
            tz = lastdp[i]
            if len(tz) == 0:
                continue

            hide = min(i, num)
            tb = sum(x[1])
            acc = 0

                la = x[0] * (num - j)
                lb = tb - acc

        for y in x:

    return res
